################################################################################
### 
### Calling program 'prsom':
### 	prsom [options] <LearnFile> <MapFile> <FilePrefix>
### 
### Arguments:
###         <LearnFile> ....... fichier de formes a classer.
###         <MapFile> ......... fichier des poids issue de SOM.
###         <FilePrefix> ...... prefix des fichiers de sortie qui seront :
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_Wei.map ........ poids de la carte.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_WeiCard.map .... poids + cardinalite pour Sammon.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_WeiVar.map ..... poids + variance pour Sammon.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_Card.res ....... cardinalite chaque neurone.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_Var.res ........ variance de chaque neurone.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_WFEP.res ....... neurone gagnant par forme.
###              - <FilePrefix>_PRSOM_Proba.res ...... activation de chaque exemple
###                dans la fonction densite de chaque neurone.
### 
### List of options:
###                 -test-file <TestSetFileName> :
###                                  to indicate the name of the
###                                  file to test. Default = NULL.
###                 -var-file <VariancesFileName> :
###                                  to indicate the name of the variances
###                                  map file to test. Default = NULL.
###                 -map-size <MapDim> <MapSize1> .. <MapSizeN> :
###                                  Map dimension and size.
###                                  Default = 2 dimensions, 10x10
###                 -map-min <MapMinString> :
###                                  string with min map value.
###                                  Default = "{-1, -1, -1, -1, -1}"
###                 -map-max <MapMaxString> :
###                                  string with max map value.
###                                  Default = "{1, 1, 1, 1, 1}"
###                 -cycles-var <NbCyclesVar> <FrequenceTestsVar> :
###                                  Number of learning cycles and test frequency (in cycles)
###                                  for Variance computation. Default = [50, 1].
###                 -smooth-dist-var <SmoothDistanceValVar> :
###                                  Value of smooth distance for Variance
###                                  computation. Default = 3.0.
###                 -cycles-mean <NbCyclesMean> <FrequenceTestsMean> :
###                                  Number of learning cycles and test frequency (in cycles)
###                                  for Mean computation. Default = [200, 10].
###                 -smooth-dist-mean <SmoothDistanceMeanMaximum> <SmoothDistanceMeanMinimum> :
###                                  Maximal and minimal value of smooth
###                                  distance for Mean computation. Default = [1.0, 0.1].
### 
################################################################################
